name: Tree Fucker
description:
HAVE YOU EVER WANTED TO FUCK A TREE? OF COURSE YOU HAVE! TREES ARE HOT!

That's why I created TREE FUCKER, a multiplayer simulator where you FUCK TREES!

That's right, I said multiplayer! You don't just fuck trees, you compete with other people to see who can fuck the most trees in a given amount of time!

And if you want to compete against your friends, you can create your own rooms, with support for up to 4 players!

Download today!
